------------------------------------------------------------------------------
"dev_boxer" by pontikkapannu 
		a.k.a. dev_measure 
		a.k.a. dod_pelaaja 
		a.k.a. Jappe
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Simple orange map made only with dev_measure textures. 
Designed for quick team death match 6 vs. 6, I suggest setting the buy time
long enough to players getting weapons they want. Or... you can play
this map with only AWPs /nades /knives /pistols, or try with shotguns only.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Including: 
	-6 terrorist spawns
	-6 counter-terrorist spawns
	-and yes I remembered to make buy zone for both sides.

	MADE FOR 6 VS. 6 GAMES!!!
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
